The scope of works at these Sites may include structural remediation, corrosion protection, pavement upgrades, and the reinstatement of critical maritime infrastructure elements. This could involve activities such as pile wrapping and repairs, cathodic protection system upgrades, pavement and deck rehabilitation, and the restoration of mooring and berthing systems. In some locations, further investigation may be required to confirm the extent of deterioration and finalise the scope.
